quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  28,85,"Inna allathee farada AAalaykaalqur-ana laradduka ila maAAadin qulrabbee aAAlamu man jaa bilhuda waman huwafee dalalin mubeen"
  28,86,"Wama kunta tarjoo an yulqailayka alkitabu illa rahmatan min rabbikafala takoonanna thaheeran lilkafireen"
  28,87,"Wala yasuddunnaka AAan ayatiAllahi baAAda ith onzilat ilayka wadAAu ilarabbika wala takoonanna mina almushrikeen"
  28,88,"Wala tadAAu maAAa Allahi ilahanakhara la ilaha illa huwa kullushay-in halikun illa wajhahu lahu alhukmuwa-ilayhi turjaAAoon"
  29,1,"Alif-lam-meem"
  29,2,"Ahasiba annasu anyutrakoo an yaqooloo amanna wahum layuftanoon"
  29,3,"Walaqad fatanna allatheena minqablihim falayaAAlamanna Allahu allatheena sadaqoowalayaAAlamanna alkathibeen"
  29,4,"Am hasiba allatheenayaAAmaloona assayyi-ati an yasbiqoona saama yahkumoon"
  29,5,"Man kana yarjoo liqaa Allahifa-inna ajala Allahi laatin wahuwa assameeAAualAAaleem"
  29,6,"Waman jahada fa-innama yujahidulinafsihi inna Allaha laghaniyyun AAani alAAalameen"
